===簽證===
{{see also|古巴簽證政策|{{link-en|古巴公民簽證要求|Visa requirements for Cuban citizens}}|越南簽證政策|越南公民簽證要求}}
兩國公民皆須申請簽證方可入境對方國家。持有{{link-en|古巴護照|Cuban passport}}的[[古巴人口|古巴公民]]可以申請電子簽證入境越南，停留不超過30天。若前往[[富国岛|富国岛]]，可在岛上免签证停留30天。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://discoverphuquoc.com/customsvisas.html#a4 |title=Phu Quoc Specific Decisions |accessdate=2020-08-24 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223162312/http://discoverphuquoc.com/customsvisas.html#a4 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vietseatourist.vn/News/category1/news-57/No-visa-required-for-tourists-to-Phu-Quoc-on-short-stay.html |title=No visa required for tourists to Phu Quoc on short stay |access-date=2014-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701095940/http://www.vietseatourist.vn/News/category1/news-57/No-visa-required-for-tourists-to-Phu-Quoc-on-short-stay.html |archive-date=2017-07-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.phuquocislandguide.com/phu-quoc-visa/#2015-vietnam-visa-updates|title=Phu Quoc visa policy|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2017-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223042509/https://www.phuquocislandguide.com/phu-quoc-visa/#2015-vietnam-visa-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref>

持[[越南護照|越南護照]]的[[越南人口|越南公民]]需向古巴的大使館、領事館、旅行社或航空公司申請「觀光卡」（西班牙語：Tarjeta del Turista）方可入境古巴，停留不超過30天。<ref name="tim">{{Timatic Visa Policy|accessdate=2017-04-01}}</ref>

古巴公民持有外交護照、公务普通护照或普通护照上标记有“公务用途”者前往越南无需办理签证。而越南公民持有外交護照、公务普通护照或普通护照上标记有“公务用途”者前往越南亦无需办理签证。

